title: No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
OB: When scripting a data set, there are no objects listed under the Context section in the palette.
EB:
Expected result: The objects under the Context section should be visible in the palette when scripting a data set. Additionally, the BeforeOpen() function should also be included.
Actual result: There are no objects listed under the Context section in the palette.
The relative bug is 126110.
